<div>
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">About Us</h1>
<p style="display: block; clear: both;"><strong>The information below are from the open data source of Winnipeg.</strong></p><br>
<p>The Park and Open Space and Park Assets Inventory has an association through the park_id. One park has many park assets, and has one to zero pool
    & spray pad.</p>
<br>
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Park and Open Space</h2>
      <div class="ml-4">
      <p>This dataset has information about all the parks and open spaces around Winnipeg.
      This includes the park name, address, district neighbourhood, electoral ward,
      and the measurement of the parkâ€™s area.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside m-2">
        <strong>Table: park_names</strong>
	       <li>park_id, park_name
	           address, location_description,
	           linear_park_system, district,
          <br>
	           neighbourhood, electoral_ward,
	           cca, area_in_hectares,
	           water_in_hectares, land_area_in_hectares</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    <br>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Park Assets</h2>
      <div class="ml-4">
      <p>This dataset has the asset inventory for the parks such as benches and play structures.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside m-2">
        <strong>Table: park_assets</strong>
	       <li>asset_id, asset_class, asset_type,
             park_id, park_name, primary_field</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    <br>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Pools</h2>
      <div class="ml-4">
      <p>This dataset has the information of the outdoor swimming pools in Winnipeg and its amenities.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside m-2">
        <strong>Table: pools</strong>
	       <li>id, park_id, park_name, address, is_open,
             avg_temp, group_bookings, lockers, slide,
             diving_board, lap_swim,
             <br>
             lessons, spray,
             showers, parking_lot, booking_info, locker_info, complex_id
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    <br>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Spray Pad</h2>
      <div class="ml-4">
      <p>This dataset has the park names where spray pads are available and if it is open.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside m-2">
        <strong>Table: spray_pads</strong>
	       <li>id, park_id, park_name, address, is_open,
             complex_id
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br>
      </div>
  </div>
